{"tid":924213,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"發覺好多人都錯呢啲常用英文嘢","createTime":"2018-12-02T02:26:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-04T16:52:04.000Z","uid":188418,"like":13,"dislike":56,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"b9c4b3b9a843084348a44caaa95351aa66464b86","tid":924213,"uid":188418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T02:26:54.000Z","msg":"發覺好多人都錯呢啲常見、常用英文嘢<br />\n無論口講定係打出嚟<br />\n所以揀咗呢四個真係好common嘅錯誤<br />\n希望大家以後可以用返啱<br />\n<br />\n1. Common<br />\n第一個就梗係common呢個字啦<br />\n雖然呢個應該好多人都知<br />\n唔係讀cum 而係&rdquo;dot com&rdquo;個&rdquo;com&rdquo;<br />\n但有時口快真係會讀咗「襟聞」<br />\n同埋個&rdquo;com&rdquo;應該相對讀得短促啲而又重啲<br />\n因為個重音喺開頭<br />\n<br />\n2. Thanks god<br />\n當一件好好嘅事發生喺你身上你就會多謝上天<br />\n但見到好多人成日講/打&rdquo;Thanks god&rdquo;真係好哽耳同令人好炆<br />\n如果你想表達畀其他人聽你感謝上帝就應該講&rdquo;Thank God&rdquo;<br />\n有加s呢個&ldquo;Thanks God&rdquo;只會用到喺代名詞後面 He, She, It嗰啲後面<br />\n或者喺你開口直接同上帝講嗰陣 你就應該講&rdquo;Thanks, God&rdquo; 或者打出嚟嗰陣打&rdquo;Thanks, God&rdquo;<br />\n注意係有逗號嘅<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. Congratulation<br />\n當你啲親戚有咩喜慶結婚或者喺某啲事上面成功咗 你都會恭喜佢哋啦<br />\n通常都會打中文「恭喜哂」或者英文&rdquo;Congratulations&rdquo; 通常打英文 你打到&rdquo;Cong&rdquo;就有predictive text彈出嚟 你一㩒就會變咗成個字出嚟<br />\n但見過有人真係打&rdquo;Congratulation&rdquo;出嚟<br />\n你祝人嗰陣只會係&rdquo;Congratulations&rdquo;<br />\n記得老師係咁教 你真心想祝人嗰陣都唔會只係祝一下啦<br />\n<br />\n4. Twelve/Twenty<br />\n眼見起碼十個人有三個唔識讀十二同二十<br />\n成日用「初/抄/差」開頭嗰個音讀<br />\n正確應該係用「他/滔/拖」個開頭再好快讀welve同wenty"},{"pid":"fe5756c32bb3cbcb36e56c9da7504e300ce8a19c","tid":924213,"uid":21423,"like":7,"dislike":32,"score":-25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T02:33:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9e2a6c3f4df83dc85b7941025ddc32229bfd4c47","tid":924213,"uid":78429,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T02:38:35.000Z","msg":"1同4打出嚟係點錯法"},{"pid":"42f5b375bbfedfab0df7c3b0904070e7a8e9949c","tid":924213,"uid":164364,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T03:29:05.000Z","msg":"無知一問<br />\nThanks god 呢度個 thanks<br />\n點解要加s既？唔可以就咁thank?"},{"pid":"9c58ceab15c3a84b3771915741cef119bf184930","tid":924213,"uid":189507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T03:42:49.000Z","msg":"有用就有錯！嘥氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71593d2d4a9bc126e435b40edd777d6cf5707ab4","tid":924213,"uid":147664,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T03:45:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無知一問<br />\nThanks god 呢度個 thanks<br />\n點解要加s既？唔可以就咁thank?</blockquote><br />\n佢咪就係話唔洗s囉 你有無讀架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58c66f1bd9c2a30fbe34b1f67738c1ec726f82b0","tid":924213,"uid":140092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T04:13:12.000Z","msg":"Th 音 --＞ F 音<br />\ne.g. Thank you ---＞ Fang Q<br />\n<br />\n-tion, -sion 重音化<br />\ne.g. Radia-唇"},{"pid":"f1f54752b21f394da395590da29c132ff26dcac0","tid":924213,"uid":192491,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T04:18:08.000Z","msg":"Thank q god"},{"pid":"7ecac56eb17036da8cb4f0174be0fbf51b967caa","tid":924213,"uid":204917,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T04:27:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2f34b52d975c228694fb330a8dd938c685be43e0","tid":924213,"uid":200247,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T04:30:25.000Z","msg":"D屎飛V骨！花橋！"},{"pid":"a471da376dc9332923c6a738b53a80382455969c","tid":924213,"uid":174295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T04:34:05.000Z","msg":"thank you you"},{"pid":"8e35fa22c4554462bad76008bebaa81c9329ce65","tid":924213,"uid":192491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T04:34:30.000Z","msg":"thanks you"},{"pid":"faee48b517b5840884974bfd2b28a8ff7caf8431","tid":924213,"uid":158499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9c4b3b9a843084348a44caaa95351aa66464b86","tid":924213,"uid":188418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T02:26: